<section class="makers-hero"></section>

<section class="hero-text">
  <span class="hero-badge">Innovation Lab</span>

  <h1>
    Makers Zone with
    <span>Hand Tools & Power Prototyping</span>
  </h1>

  <p>
    The Makers Zone with Hand Tools & Power Prototyping is a collaborative workspace
    designed for innovators, students, and creators to transform their ideas into
    working prototypes. Equipped with a variety of hand tools and power tools,
    this zone allows participants to design, build, and experiment with different
    materials and components.
  </p>
</section>



